  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MOBILE2 is a randomized controlled trial comparing mechanical and oral antibiotic bowel
      preparation to mechanical bowel preparation only in patients undergoing anterior rectal
      resection with primary anastomosis. Primary endpoint is Comprehensive Complication Index
      within 30 days from surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
